# math_showcase_delims_smoke.numos — Phase 10B. Cycle the Math Showcase to the
# cases with TALL delimiters — (2/3)^2 (index 4) and (1 + 1/2)/(x + 3) (index 6) —
# where the parenthesis height exceeds the single bundled stix_math size variant
# and the vector delimiter fallback (MathRenderer::drawStrokedDelimiter) renders.
# Used to visually confirm the delimiters look clean / font-quality, not jagged.
# Warning-only (screenshots, no golden).
log "showcase delims: start"
wait 200
open_app MathShowcase
wait 60
# RIGHT x4 -> case 4: (2/3)^2
key right
key right
key right
key right
wait 20
screenshot out/showcase_case_2over3_sq.ppm
# RIGHT x2 -> case 6: (1 + 1/2)/(x + 3)
key right
key right
wait 20
screenshot out/showcase_case_nested.ppm
assert_app MathShowcase
log "showcase delims: captured"
